section.div: Resume Matcher is an open source, free tool to improve your resume. It works by using AI, Reader LLMs, to compare and rank resumes with job descriptions.
Enhance your résumé with Large Language Models
🌌 A complete search engine and RAG pipeline in your browser, server or edge network with support for full-text, vector, and hybrid search in less than 2kb.
